_sText:
This is the update to the original gg_deagle5_assault_ck Inspired by the original deagle5! Here is a list of fixes
Fixed env_cubemaps Added rope to catwalk so it was no longer floating Added playerclip along catwalk so players would no longer get stuck Added partial skybox around map to fix glitch when you went outside map boundaries Added a second spawn camera Fixed lighting issues Fixed placement of lights on catwalk
Special thanks to HacksawJack For the screenshots and custom logo. Thanks to my friends at DangerZone who help me out! Enjoy!!! -Nosoul!
